      • addMenu

        public static final void addMenu(org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Shell shell,
           App[] Apps,
           java.lang.String version)
        Adds a menu to the input Shell. Adds a File menu, Commands menu, Telemetry menu, and Help menu. Note: This method is called twice: once upon launching of the program, and once again when Apps are populated. The first time this is called there are no Apps and the Command and Telemetry menus are consequently empty. The second time this is called, the option to Populate Apps in the File menu is absent.
        Parameters:
        shell - The Shell to add the menu to.
        Apps - The Apps to add to the menu.
        version - The version of this program.
